sentences: Patrick Davin (16 February 1962 – 9 September 2020) was a Belgian orchestra conductor.
He served as musical and artistic director of the Orchestre symphonique de Mulhouse from 2013 to 2020.
In July 2020, he became director of the music department of the Royal Conservatory of Liège.
Patrick Davin died in Brussels on 9 September 2020 at the age of 58.
